e., a regime represented by several fractions with different stopping times.\nFormulas for computing the gas and dust velocities for polydisperse dust with\neach fraction exchanging momentum with the gas are presented.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Aug 2018 17:14:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-09"}
