onal cost to $O(R^2\nN_d\\log^2 N) +O(R^3 N_d \\log N)+ O(P^2 N\\log N)$ for the preconditioned system.\nWe present several numerical tests to illustrate the proposed algorithm using\n$h$ and $p$ refinements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Aug 2018 20:57:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-10"}
