 near their present, close-in locations. One\nexplanation that is consistent with the similar fundamental properties of\nsingles and multis is that many of the singles are members of multi-planet\nsystems that underwent planet-planet scattering.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Aug 2018 03:51:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 9 Oct 2018 22:54:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-13"}
