d demonstrate that the\ntopological edge mode avoids defects, and that the propagation direction of the\nmode can be reversed by inverting the applied magnetic field. Our\nexciton-polariton TI paves the way for a variety of new topological phenomena,\nas they involve light-matter interaction, gain, and perhaps most importantly -\nexciton-polaritons interact with one another as a nonlinear many-body system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Aug 2018 14:24:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-21"}
